        rdfs:comment      "Rationale: The protein co-purifies with post-synaptic densities in a purification scheme starting from juvenile mouse hippocampus, and is identified by mass spectrometry.\n- The protein is listed in Sup.Table S12 tab \"other fractions\" with the name IF1AX (Eukaryotic translation initiation factor 1A, X-chromosomal), row 2433.. Experimental description: \"juvenile mouse hippocampus\"" ;
